data.oai_dc:dc: PISCO: Intertidal: Barnacle Fecundity Monitoring: UCSC: 2008

This metadata record documents the barnacle fecundity data for the PISCO intertidal surveys. The reproductive state of two barnacle species is monitored monthly at intertidal PISCO central California sites.
